Synopsis:
Upon interacting with the tentacle living inside the tower's wall, player is faced with several options to choose from. 
- Take a sample (can be used in Mig mini quest)
- Poke to see how it reacts
- Examine it to learn more about it
- Tear it down with brute force
Damage being done onto the tentacle will trigger a reaction from the Absolute
